You look great.

01:58.472 --> 02:01.831
- Can I get you a drink?
- Look, Michael, I don't...

02:04.753 --> 02:07.003
Jesus.

02:07.038 --> 02:09.122
I forgot.

02:09.174 --> 02:11.507
It's not even your real name.

02:14.212 --> 02:16.713
It's, uh... Lenny.

02:19.184 --> 02:22.301
Lenny.

02:22.354 --> 02:25.054
So tell me what's going on.

02:25.106 --> 02:28.224
How advanced is it?

02:28.226 --> 02:31.060
I already emailed my
friend at Sloan Kettering.

02:31.112 --> 02:32.528
If it's as serious as you say...

02:32.564 --> 02:34.981
- Krista. Krista.
- Then she wants to...

02:35.033 --> 02:36.232
Look.

02:40.372 --> 02:41.704
I'm not dying.

02:45.160 --> 02:47.126
You're a sick motherfucker!

02:47.162 --> 02:48.202
Look, hold on. It's the only way

02:48.203 --> 02:49.960
- I could get you to meet up.
- Don't you ever call me again,

02:49.961 --> 02:53.102
- even when you are dying.
- One of your patients hacked me.

02:53.635 --> 02:55.501
Some kid.

02:55.553 --> 02:58.421
His name's Elliot Alderson.

02:58.423 --> 03:01.174
I went to the police already.

03:01.226 --> 03:04.260
Please sit back down.

03:04.262 --> 03:06.145
We need to talk about this.

03:17.158 --> 03:20.193
Here. The police had
their cyber crime division

03:20.245 --> 03:21.778
look into it.

03:21.830 --> 03:26.115
They've been trying to track
him down for the past six weeks.

03:26.117 --> 03:28.035
- What is this?
- That proves it was him.

03:28.036 --> 03:30.286
He took my dog to the vet.

03:30.288 --> 03:33.289
Look. See, she was microchipped,

03:33.341 --> 03:36.843
and I gave her chip number
to all the vets in the city.

03:39.631 --> 03:43.349
This sick fucker not only
hacked me and ruined my life,

03:43.384 --> 03:45.134
he stole my dog on top of it.

03:47.605 --> 03:48.967
This guy's certifiable.

03:48.968 --> 03:52.191
I mean, he's seeing you,
so technically he is.

03:52.192 --> 03:58.043
- What did he do to you exactly?
- He made me...

04:00.618 --> 04:03.569
you know...

04:03.621 --> 04:05.822
say all those things to you.

04:10.295 --> 04:13.129
This kid should not be
allowed to do what he did.

04:13.164 --> 04:16.332
He hacked into my private life.

04:16.334 --> 04:19.084
And then that Ashley
Madison leak happened.

04:19.137 --> 04:22.505
My wife found out about
everything anyway.

04:22.507 --> 04:25.141
After the whole thing, she left me.

04:25.176 --> 04:27.477
I can't even see my little girl.

04:27.512 --> 04:31.363
- The divorce is... is a nightmare.
- I don't give a shit about your divorce.

04:31.364 --> 04:33.015
Look, if he's doing this to me,

04:33.067 --> 04:36.185
then he must be doing this to other people.

04:36.187 --> 04:37.687
Think about it.

04:37.689 --> 04:40.656
If he knew enough
about me to hack me,

04:40.692 --> 04:43.910
then that means he must
have hacked you, too.

04:46.414 --> 04:48.865
He did, didn't he?

04:58.009 --> 05:03.504
- I can't talk about this with you.
- Hey! You have to help me catch him.

05:05.049 --> 05:06.849
The dog thing alone isn't enough.

05:06.885 --> 05:10.136
My buddy says this
Computer Abuse and Fraud Act

05:10.188 --> 05:11.721
is tough to prosecute.

05:11.773 --> 05:14.190
You need a lot of evidence.

05:14.225 --> 05:16.309
This kid is good, Krista.

05:16.361 --> 05:19.862
He was routing through something
called proxies or something

05:19.898 --> 05:20.897
out in Estonia.

05:20.899 --> 05:22.231
He's untraceable.

05:22.283 --> 05:24.400
Short of that whole
country falling apart,

05:24.402 --> 05:27.153
we're never gonna get our
hands on any real evidence.

05:27.205 --> 05:33.680
- Just what exactly do you think I can do?
- Maybe he said something.

05:34.879 --> 05:37.413
You know, in your sessions.

05:37.415 --> 05:40.499
Oh, come on, don't give me that
privileged information bullshit.

05:40.552 --> 05:42.835
This guy's committing
a crime, a serious one.

05:42.887 --> 05:45.254
He deserves to go to jail.

05:45.306 --> 05:47.974
If you know something,

05:48.009 --> 05:50.593
if he said anything,
you have to tell me.

05:52.096 --> 05:55.932
Look, I'm not the enemy here.

05:55.934 --> 05:59.101
He is.

05:59.103 --> 06:01.687
We were a good thing.

06:01.739 --> 06:03.606
Remember?

06:03.608 --> 06:06.943
I mean, don't you remember this place?

06:08.663 --> 06:11.948
We had some good times here.

06:11.950 --> 06:14.116
Come on.

06:16.120 --> 06:20.089
Don't stay mad at me.

06:20.124 --> 06:21.958
I really loved you.

06:26.264 --> 06:29.465
He never told me anything.

06:29.517 --> 06:31.934
I can't help you.

06:40.478 --> 06:43.479
The asshole stole my dog!

