09:12.096 --> 09:14.764
Wait, I don't even trust you.

09:19.470 --> 09:20.469
Hey.

09:20.471 --> 09:22.221
Hey, where you going?

09:22.273 --> 09:25.107
What about your car?

09:25.143 --> 09:29.145
Hey, we're gonna tow your car tonight!

09:57.308 --> 10:00.370
- What took you so long?
- I just had to shower and change.

10:00.371 --> 10:04.146
You're still new here. I wouldn't push it.

10:25.503 --> 10:27.453
Jesus Christ, finally you're here.

10:27.505 --> 10:29.337
- Where have you been?
- Yeah, man.

10:29.338 --> 10:31.674
I mean, not cool, not cool at all.

10:31.709 --> 10:33.375
I thought we were
gonna execute together.

10:33.377 --> 10:35.044
I mean, what is going on here?

10:35.096 --> 10:37.179
He's just saying that we
had planned on something

10:37.215 --> 10:39.684
- a little more ceremonial.
- Ceremonial? Man,

10:39.685 --> 10:40.799
we been wiping drives,

10:40.852 --> 10:43.302
wrangling cables, pulling
fiber taps and the...

10:43.354 --> 10:44.553
Okay, everyone, lay off!

10:44.555 --> 10:46.522
I'm sure he had his reasons.

10:46.557 --> 10:48.891
Besides, whatever. The
point is, it worked.

10:48.893 --> 10:51.227
- Jesus, what did I do?
- We need to clean up

10:51.229 --> 10:52.645
and get the hell out of here.

10:52.697 --> 10:54.396
Were you there? Did you see it?

10:54.448 --> 10:57.213
- What did I do?
- Elliot, what's going on?

10:57.214 --> 10:59.203
You disappear on me at the apartment

10:59.204 --> 11:01.570
and come here to execute
without even telling me.

11:01.622 --> 11:04.490
Execute. It executed, but how?

11:04.542 --> 11:06.588
- I... what happened to Tyrell?
- Then you were gone

11:06.589 --> 11:08.994
for another three days.

11:09.046 --> 11:14.815
- Where have you been?
- Are you saying... it went through?

11:15.086 --> 11:17.219
Like gangbusters.

11:17.255 --> 11:18.837
People are loving it.

11:18.890 --> 11:21.340
They actually want to join fsociety.

11:21.392 --> 11:25.010
Elliot, they're organizing
protests all across the city.

