18:28.156 --> 18:30.123
I didn't mean anything by it.

18:30.158 --> 18:32.334
- I was just trying to...
- Never mind what you meant.

18:32.335 --> 18:33.709
Just do as I say.

18:38.633 --> 18:41.801
I'm sorry.

18:41.836 --> 18:44.220
I didn't mean to snap at you.

18:44.255 --> 18:46.172
It's been a long day,

18:46.174 --> 18:49.892
and... and I'm not used to
all the new faces around here.

18:51.930 --> 18:53.513
No problem.

18:53.565 --> 18:55.515
Four minutes, people!

18:55.567 --> 18:57.850
Let's get last looks. Let's go.

18:57.852 --> 19:01.988
So anyways, this should
fry anything and everything

19:02.023 --> 19:03.189
to a crisp.

19:03.191 --> 19:04.524
You're in luck. My boss is at the bank.

19:04.576 --> 19:06.192
Seems like everybody's
lining up this morning.

19:06.244 --> 19:08.411
So you got some time.

19:08.446 --> 19:09.743
Jesus,

19:09.744 --> 19:13.249
- are we really doing this right now?
- Hey, I don't need no judgment.

19:13.284 --> 19:14.917
Not like I want to be here either.

19:14.953 --> 19:17.670
Sorry, dude, I got no sympathy.

19:17.705 --> 19:20.506
You don't want to put cute
puppies out of their misery,

19:20.542 --> 19:22.425
you don't have to.

19:22.460 --> 19:23.709
That's just sick.

19:23.761 --> 19:25.261
That ain't on me. I gotta pay the bills.

19:25.296 --> 19:27.547
That's the only reason why I'm here.

19:51.122 --> 19:54.624
You know, I've run all the scenarios

19:54.659 --> 19:59.128
of our little revolution here, but, uh...

19:59.164 --> 20:02.748
using a dead puppy oven was not on my list.

21:20.995 --> 21:23.496
Can I help you?

21:32.674 --> 21:33.839
Yeah.

21:33.891 --> 21:36.676
Looking for Tyrell Wellick.

21:36.728 --> 21:40.612
- Is he here?
- No.

21:41.015 --> 21:43.933
